Classes in itec.minicompiler.SymbolTable used by itec.minicompiler
Symbol
          The Symbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable.
SymbolTable
          The SymbolTable implements a linked list of Symbols the Parser uses to maintain the structure of the Symbols given by the source code and to do the scoping.
Type
          The Type implements a type a Symbol in the SymbolTable can have.

Type
          The Type implements a type a Symbol in the SymbolTable can have.
TypedSymbol
          The TypedSymbol implements a Symbol in the SymbolTable which has also a Type in addition to the Symbol-attributes.
